-- my-ds.page: Creating A Page

In this section, we will learn about creating pages in `doc-site`.

The `page` component empowers you to create **one-off standalone pages**. You can
use other fastn components, or markdown.


-- ds.h3: ðŸ’¡ How to create a new page?

Create a new `.ftd` file into your `fastn` project. Add `page` component inside
`.ftd` file as shown below.

Click on download icon of below code-block. `sample.ftd` file will be
downloaded. Add this file inside your `fastn` project and deploy or run `fastn
serve` on your localhost. Access your localhost in browser
e.g.`http://127.0.0.1:8000/sample/` you will see below page output.

